title: High Elo Ranked Team
body: Comment your interest in joining a high elo ranked team, that could possibly contend in the OOL, OCS and maybe eventually OOL. Trials are for anybody Platinum or above. All roles accepted.

replies.body: I was plat but decayed back to gold from inactivity. Am I eligible to join? Gold 1 75 LP at the moment. Plat last season as well.
